node.text:
Watch as @kveeks rescues a scared but sweet dog from the side of a 120 ft cliff. Poor doggo was stuck there for nearly 3 days. He is doing fine now but @kveeks has hundreds of fire ant 🔥 🐜 bites all over him... proof that no good deed goes unpunished!  8 minute video but well worth the watch. It will restore your faith in humanity. 
Big Island, Hawaii
Video by @kveeks
